Recording artist Sia performs onstage at the 2016 iHeartRadio Music Festival at T-Mobile Arena on September 23, 2016 in Las Vegas, Nevada. JOHANNESBURG - Singer and songwriter Sia performed "Elastic Heart" during Kanye West's weekly church service in LA. In a clip shared on social media by Kim Kardashian West the Australian singer emerges from the background without her signature over-sized wig to join the choir as they sing an updated version of the song. READ: Kanye West to bring his Sunday Service to Coachella Sia is the latest celebrity to join Kanye's exclusive services which Kim has described in an interview with Elle as a "a healing experience" for her husband. The 41-year-old rapper recently brought his Sunday service to Coachella, which received rave reviews.